Class VPFDatabase

  • java.lang.Object
    • gov.nasa.worldwind.avlist.AVListImpl
      • gov.nasa.worldwind.formats.vpf.VPFDatabase
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    AVList

    public class VPFDatabase
extends AVListImpl
    DIGEST Part 2, Annex C.2.2.2.5 and C.2.3.6:
    A database is a collection of related libraries and additional tables. The library attribute table acts as a table of contents for the database. Database information is contained in a database header table. Database level data quality information can be maintained in the data quality table.
